    'techOverview.pageTitle': "[ES] H365 Technical Overview",
    'techOverview.section1.title': "[ES] 1. Introduction",
    'techOverview.section1.content': "[ES] H365 is a modern, web-based hospital management system designed to streamline clinical workflows, improve patient care coordination, and provide robust data management capabilities for healthcare facilities. Built with a focus on user experience and scalability, H365 aims to support healthcare professionals in delivering efficient and effective patient care.",
    'techOverview.section2.title': "[ES] 2. Technology Stack",
    'techOverview.section2.itemFrontend.title': "[ES] Frontend",
    'techOverview.section2.itemFrontend.desc': "[ES] Next.js (App Router), React, TypeScript: Utilizes the latest Next.js features for optimal performance and developer experience, combined with React's component-based architecture and TypeScript for strong typing and code maintainability.",
    'techOverview.section2.itemUI.title': "[ES] UI Components",
    'techOverview.section2.itemUI.desc': "[ES] ShadCN UI: A collection of beautifully designed, accessible, and customizable components built on Radix UI and Tailwind CSS, enabling rapid development of a consistent user interface.",
    'techOverview.section2.itemStyling.title': "[ES] Styling",
    'techOverview.section2.itemStyling.desc': "[ES] Tailwind CSS: A utility-first CSS framework that allows for rapid UI development directly in the markup, ensuring consistency and easy customization.",
    'techOverview.section2.itemAI.title': "[ES] Artificial Intelligence (AI) Integration",
    'techOverview.section2.itemAI.desc': "[ES] Genkit: Leverages Genkit, a Firebase framework, to integrate with Google AI models (like Gemini) for features such as treatment recommendations and decision support.",
    'techOverview.section2.itemState.title': "[ES] State Management",
    'techOverview.section2.itemState.desc': "[ES] React Context and Component-level State: Employs React's built-in Context API for global state needs (e.g., Locale, Theme, Sidebar) and component-level state for local UI logic, ensuring efficient data flow and component reusability.",
    'techOverview.section2.itemDeployment.title': "[ES] Deployment",
    'techOverview.section2.itemDeployment.desc': "[ES] (Deployed on Vercel for prototype): The application is structured for easy deployment on modern cloud platforms specializing in Next.js applications, ensuring scalability and reliability.",
    'techOverview.section2.subsectionFrontendArch.title': "[ES] 2.1. Frontend Architecture Overview",
    'techOverview.section2.subsectionFrontendArch.desc': "[ES] The frontend is built using Next.js with the App Router, promoting a modular structure with Server and Client Components. React provides the component-based UI, styled with Tailwind CSS and ShadCN UI components. Global state (like theme and locale) is managed via React Context, while local component state handles UI interactions. AI features are integrated using Genkit, typically invoked through Server Actions.",
    'techOverview.section3.title': "[ES] 3. Core Modules and Key Features",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.title': "[ES] 3.1. Dashboard",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemOverview.title': "[ES] Centralized Overview",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemOverview.desc': "[ES] Provides a real-time, at-a-glance view of critical hospital metrics, activities, and alerts, enabling administrators and staff to quickly assess the current operational status and make informed decisions.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemSummaryCards.title': "[ES] Summary Cards",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemSummaryCards.desc': "[ES] Displays key performance indicators such as Today's Appointments, Ward Occupancy, ER Status, New Patient counts, Total Patients, Common Conditions, Top 5 Prescriptions, and Drafted Consultations, offering immediate insights.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemQuickActions.title': "[ES] Quick Actions",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemQuickActions.desc': "[ES] Offers direct links to frequently used modules and tasks (Register Patient, Schedule Appointment, AI Consultation, Manage Wards, Lab Dashboard, Maternity Records), streamlining navigation and improving user efficiency.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemVisualAnalytics.title': "[ES] Visual Analytics",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionDashboard.itemVisualAnalytics.desc': "[ES] Includes interactive charts like a Pie Chart for Patient Entry Points (Outpatient, Emergency, Epidemic Alert) and a Bar Chart for Daily Patient Attendance, facilitating data-driven understanding of hospital operations.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionPatientReg.title': "[ES] 3.2. Patient Registration",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionPatientReg.itemIndividualBulk.title': "[ES] Individual & Bulk Registration",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionPatientReg.itemIndividualBulk.desc': "[ES] Supports comprehensive data entry for individual patients (including National ID, demographics, contact info, next of kin, allergies, chronic conditions) and allows for efficient registration of multiple patients through CSV file uploads, catering to various intake scenarios.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionPatientReg.itemPhotoCapture.title': "[ES] Photo Capture",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionPatientReg.itemPhotoCapture.desc': "[ES] Features integrated webcam functionality for capturing patient photos directly in the registration form (formatted to a passport-like aspect ratio), enhancing patient identification.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionVisitingPatients.title': "[ES] 3.3. Visiting Patients (Consultation Intake)",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionVisitingPatients.itemSearchModal.title': "[ES] Patient Search & Quick Registration",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionVisitingPatients.itemSearchModal.desc': "[ES] Allows staff to quickly search for existing patients by National ID. If a patient is not found, a modal enables rapid registration of essential details (National ID, Name, DOB, Gender, Chronic Conditions) to streamline the intake process.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionVisitingPatients.itemVisitEntry.title': "[ES] Visit Entry & Waiting List",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionVisitingPatients.itemVisitEntry.desc': "[ES] Facilitates recording the department, reason for visit, and assigned doctor, automatically adding the patient to the relevant waiting list for consultation or service. Displays mock analytics for daily visits.",
    'techOverview.section3.subsectionAppointments.title': "[ES] 3.4. Appointments",
