    'techOverview.section4.title': "[ES] 4. UI/UX Style Guidelines",
    'techOverview.section4.itemPrimaryColor.title': "[ES] Primary Color",
    'techOverview.section4.itemPrimaryColor.desc': "[ES] Vibrant Blue (HSL: 210 90% 50%): Used for default buttons and key interactive elements, chosen for its professional and trustworthy association in healthcare.",
    'techOverview.section4.itemSecondaryColors.title': "[ES] Secondary Colors",
    'techOverview.section4.itemSecondaryColors.desc': "[ES] White and light grey (e.g., HSL: 210 40% 96.1%): Used for backgrounds and card surfaces to ensure a clean, uncluttered interface and enhance readability.",
    'techOverview.section4.itemAccentColor.title': "[ES] Accent Color",
    'techOverview.section4.itemAccentColor.desc': "[ES] Light Blue (HSL: 197 53% 79%): Applied to secondary interactive elements, highlights, or specific informational components to provide visual hierarchy without competing with the primary action color.",
    'techOverview.section4.itemTypography.title': "[ES] Typography",
    'techOverview.section4.itemTypography.desc': "[ES] Geist Sans: Utilized for its modern aesthetic and excellent legibility across various screen sizes and resolutions, ensuring content is easily digestible.",
    'techOverview.section4.itemLayout.title': "[ES] Layout",
    'techOverview.section4.itemLayout.desc': "[ES] Clean, organized, responsive: Employs clean and organized layouts with clear section headings for easy navigation. The design is responsive, adapting to different screen sizes for optimal viewing on desktops and tablets. Features like sticky panels are used for contextual information.",
    'techOverview.section4.itemTheme.title': "[ES] Theme",
    'techOverview.section4.itemTheme.desc': "[ES] Supports Dark, Light, and System modes: Offers user-selectable themes to cater to individual visual comfort and reduce eye strain, enhancing accessibility.",
